{"tid":1718990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講個笑話 香港人話罷工 但係個個都拎住部電腦home office","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:57:31.000Z","uid":126113,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"70678cdd072466126bf117350f55235d765c3e6d","tid":1718990,"uid":126113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"各位奴性重嘅香港人<br />\n大家都話罷工先係最有效<br />\n我想請問一下當初原意係乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一邊屌鳩出面死都要撘車返工嘅人<br />\n一邊拎住部電腦係屋企開會做嘢<br />\n我真係想請問一下呢個係咩玩法</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有公司運作繼續如常<br />\n對商家造成零威脅<br />\n罷工可以威脅到政府?<br />\n笑話嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑完繼續home office啦各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家係各大學為香港打生打死嘅同學已淪為condom"},{"pid":"74567e0ea115d2df65bc91cb4047ec150d8a5977","tid":1718990,"uid":126113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7957e3768c3e4b33c474e52e9212d7fcd5b7afa2","tid":1718990,"uid":126113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:42:48.000Z","msg":"講真話俾人負評係咩玩法"},{"pid":"05f61a47d5d3621d2924001d97fd91f5f950934f","tid":1718990,"uid":126113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:43:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae2324b3ec63ed2b8e17fde7e5495ff01f69a050","tid":1718990,"uid":126113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de173e24137d85cfde0e0ac75bd6cc06068a9273","tid":1718990,"uid":126113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3b4efae754c22112ec6e28622e5a64207ce9f27","tid":1718990,"uid":126113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:43:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c71ce6a888a09da77e33f264ef5eabf930ca